    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Define quantity of items in 'Current MaxDropDownItems' <em>TextBox </em>to display in <em>DropDown </em>of demonstrated <em>ComboBox</em>.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui ComboBox contains MaxDropDownItems property that defines max number items that will be displayed in the ComboBox DropDown menu.</p>]]></Paragraph>
